{"tid":1325844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔想警察頭破血流","createTime":"2019-07-17T04:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T04:56:14.000Z","uid":231905,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a395e021887f2a2dec0faf206fe4ba215d1035","tid":1325844,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我想佢地五勞七傷，絕子絕孫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知CCTVB同狗總最鐘意誇大狗隻受傷，如果<span style=\"color: red;\">搞到流哂狗血就麻鬼煩，畫面又唔好睇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再者如果帶利器比人周到就好撚難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以如果有需要打狗，牧童笛又好咩鈍器都好，最好就<span style=\"color: red;\">打身打手腳打到佢地內傷，個樣又睇唔出</span>就Perfect池<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   如果你地夠仆街仲可以<span style=\"color: red;\">拆佢地祠堂</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7ee774ee93621c50bc98e0dcebd1d7e44c0d6d","tid":1325844,"uid":231905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"大家記得出黎玩都要識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff74f437ff406bc7f16d19ec06d61a1ca92d7f2","tid":1325844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻你：<br />\n[緊急呼籲]今晚9點一齊上twitter將黑警濫權揚威國際，警告遊客不要來港旅遊，用經濟壓力逼使政府回應！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1325723/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1325723/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面攬炒<br />\n<br />\n9點一齊一野谷上trending <br />\n#Hongkongwarning #Fthepopo<br />\n<br />\nTwitter見！！！"},{"pid":"0b584c5100b93f1b53d3b087017334616d494a40","tid":1325844,"uid":231905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967931fc36201370e6d80b8577d4c2b7657c9257","tid":1325844,"uid":272371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"唔好打臉，阿sir個靚仔樣要上電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264db96e05e7630d29b63a5248909e3f5c1ad99d","tid":1325844,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"967931fc36201370e6d80b8577d4c2b7657c9257","tid":1325844,"uid":272371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"唔好打臉，阿sir個靚仔樣要上電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6f4a4de7ca627b1396e19aba272185193c601a","tid":1325844,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"咁即係共產黨成名技，&quot;折祠堂&quot;"},{"pid":"246b567a1bead5bef158e687697492387a2d543d","tid":1325844,"uid":132770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JvM18n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb